{"type": "article", "id": 60305, "title": "彭于晏拿下 Berluti 代言，阿迪和永久自行车联名出新年系列 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-15T05:23:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 884, "name": "品牌"}, {"id": 4489, "name": "代言"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 48802, "name": "抖音"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190115125833xXLYaIvPF1dm7RAO.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"18Xs\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/5074698188/4328287435977751\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>彭于晏担任 Berluti 品牌代言人，</b></a>Berluti 为 LVMH 旗下的法国男装及鞋履品牌。彭于晏出演的首支广告片“向往的朋友”（Aspire To Be）也同时上线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115125932yCmJBfcnOAUT5Elt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s08278xvqf6\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"iIcU\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4328461080079715?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>王嘉尔成为 Fendi 品牌形象大使，</b></a>之前古力娜扎是品牌大使。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115125948KH6rB8mQWUIj4bsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.446296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"u7Nn\"><b><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zqF41BUKLy8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">潘婷最新的广告 “HairWeGo”</a> </b>由网红婴儿 chanco 和日本广告主持人 Sato Kondo 出演。 chanco 天生发量超多，她妈妈在 instagram 上记录了她的头发生长变化，然后短时间走红，现在拥有 33 万粉丝。主持人  Kondo 虽然满头银发，也没有刻意去染发。</p><p line=\"38pj\">潘婷借此鼓励女性接纳真实的自我。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k1356xlplcn\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Ovho\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4328683801745192?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>张艺兴代言了爱奇艺 VIP 会员，</b></a>广告片运用了代言人名字的谐音梗，表示快乐要尽“兴”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j0827mqyh5v\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"kwh1\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1993299944/4328664932337115\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>今天还有吴亦凡代言了韩束面膜。</b></a>前几天，良品铺子才刚宣布了吴亦凡的代言。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130108R9Jduz2Qe7DaCKZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.236000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"yNIL\">根据 Hypebeast 报道，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2019/1/adidas-originals-yongjiu-2019-capsule-collection\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adidas Originals 联合永久牌自行车打造了 “YONGJIU” 中国新年特别系列，</a>包含运动鞋、连帽衫、外套、T-Shirt、运动裤等多款单品。设计上加入了永久自行车的 Logo 和自行车元素，有些单品还选择了具有新年气息的红色。部分单品将登陆 adidas Originals 指定店铺。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130127kMtQBR0jN5yOdhJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.264286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130127FGUSCuJeA971OYtb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.264286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130128Q8KCgmaXHucUxhyp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130128sFA9zRE3hi1gd2Wf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901151301278yYsViawRphvjJTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130129XzyuEhn2o0p7IlYB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130129FnSB7WbRDIMvuOEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130129Zfvz62NbxPkcTXUu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"ZEUu\">抖音首个商业化搜索品专区上线，合作品牌是兰蔻。在搜索栏输入“兰蔻”或者兰蔻彩妆大使“刘涛”的名字，页面即跳出品牌广告专区，点进广告就是购物页面了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130150P3hxJjv1iZcVNdrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.710667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901151301498zH0yM67s2LDqKVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.710667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"CuOq\">舒肤佳发布了温暖新年广告<b><a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/1984922885\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">“你，把父母弄丢了吗？”</a></b>用一句家庭中常讲的“回家吃饭”，向年轻人传递多关心父母、回家过年实现家人渴望团圆的想法。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x0826ih4r9u\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"8wOu\"><a href=\"http://  https://www.thedrum.com/news/2019/01/14/kinder-surprised-after-toy-makes-accidental-kkk-reference\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>健达巧克力最近发售了一批限量奇趣蛋，</b></a>然而玩具小人举着的气球上是 “KKK”。而美国种族主义代表组织 “3K 党” 的缩写也是 “KKK”，继而引发了争议。</p><p line=\"8wOu\">健达的母集团费列罗派出面道歉，并解释玩具上的标记是错误的。费列罗集团还提到，剩余的库存玩具正在被销毁，相关玩具也已经下架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190115130246tz7PD6mRCFKMYreo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"de8y\"><b><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2019/01/14/wfa-taps-pg-s-gerry-d-angelo-media-board-advertisers-cannot-relinquish-control\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">根据 The Drum 报道，WFA（世界广告主联合会，</a><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2019/01/14/wfa-taps-pg-s-gerry-d-angelo-media-board-advertisers-cannot-relinquish-control\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">World Federation of Advertisers</a><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2019/01/14/wfa-taps-pg-s-gerry-d-angelo-media-board-advertisers-cannot-relinquish-control\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">）进行了重组，</a></b>宝洁的全球媒体总监 Gerry D'Angelo 被任命为媒体论坛的联合主席。他在论坛上强调：“广告商不能放弃对媒介、数据和算法的控制。” WFA 希望解决包括广告欺诈、品牌安全、第三方验证在内的等八大问题。</p><p line=\"eMKN\"><a href=\"http://With the reverberations of that decision still echoing a bitter war of words has broken out with fallen contenders WPP and McCann attesting that DDB was not capable of delivering on the decade long brief for its fee of $136m.  The last-minute counterattack threatens to snatch victory from DDB as both sides entrench themselves behind their own army of lawyers by opening up a new front in Washington in the hope of forcing a rethink.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>根据 The Drum 报道，</b></a>WPP 和麦肯将联合参加美军账户的比稿，认为 DDB 无法以 13.6 亿美元的成本提供长达 10 年的服务。美军每年广告投放额高达 40 亿，去年宏盟集团的 DDB 击败了一直和美军服务的麦肯，以及与参与竞标的 WPP。</p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/eNZZNZA7p7c?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" rel=\"nofollow\">stephen-kraakmo</a> on unsplash<br></p>"}